title: Garmin Mobile XT Full Image For Symbian, Windows Mobile, Palm
description:
Welcome!

This is a windows executable file, that if you run, will alow you to install garmin in:

Any memory card in the computers card reader - It will install all the versions, and when you place the card in the mobile device it will select which one to install.

Any mobile device or its memory card - It will find, and install the right version for the device you have.

After you are done witht that, you have to get my other torrent where the maps and installation instructions are included ~2.5GB in size.

Unrar and follow the instructions carefuly and you will have a navigation system on your hands.

By Restrected!
Enjoy
